Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.46,0:00:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the lead, Endo!\NI haven't seen this part of the labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He one-shot that Behemoth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no shortcut?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must hurry to them by any means possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found us a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Pile Bunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pile driver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that utilizes the immense force created by\Nelectromagnetic acceleration and explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pile driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. These long rods are made\Nfrom ore compressed with Transmute,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then coated with azantium,\Nthe strongest metal in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on ahead. Follow in after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hole?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nagumo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two're still good friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, really?! Is that really you, Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Yaegashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be the cool\Nand collected one, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! I-I brought help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue, keep Endo and the others safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shea, go check out the fallen knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tio and Myu, take care of these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okey dokey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine, you stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pray let us handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never expected someone to come\Ndown to hell on their own volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't feel like dying,\Nthen get the hell outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means if you leave now, I'll let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insolent human! You'll regret your\Nfoolishness when you die by my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay. That means you're my enemy, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so, what kind of half-assed magic is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is barely street magician level.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.12,0:06:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Heal me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He targeted the healer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're the one\Nwho decided to take a trip to Hell today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard to believe, but that's Nagumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like I said, that's Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same Hajime Nagumo\Nwho fell from the bridge that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:08:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he looks way different,\Nso I can get your reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo died! You're just\Nmaking shit up for no reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw his status plate!\NThere's no doubt about it, it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've forged it or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, he's gotta\Nbe plotting something bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to get in Hajime's way again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taniguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Firmament.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...believe you lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaegashi, take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so light, but it sliced\Nthrough like it was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crashing Gaol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is checkmate, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My high-level magic meant nothing to you.\NAre you sure you're human?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said Papa, didn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, then. I'm not interested\Nin hearing your last words or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is how a demon got their hands on those\Nmonsters, and what you were doing down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm going to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:12:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me tell you what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think those monsters were\Ncreated by a form of ancient magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And demonkind gained the ability to use\Nthat ancient magic by clearing a great labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to explore the pits of the hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or rather, get to the end\Nof the great labyrinth, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. If you're anything like them,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then your monstrous appearance\Nand inhuman strength checks out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like "them," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the monsters were a gift from the guy\Nwho actually cleared the labyrinth, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that answers my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, right? Then end me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But remember this. One day,\Nmy lover will find you and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who comes for me.\NDemon or god, I'll kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyone who's just being puppeteered\Nby that god won't be able to touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Nagumo! She can't fight us anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shea, how's Meld doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we'd been one second too late,\Nwe wouldn't have been able to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We used the Holy Water just like you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but are you sure it was\Nokay to waste it? It's so rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's been a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him dying on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue! Thanks a lot for taking care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.16,0:13:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon you guys, read the room!\NEveryone's coming over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Meld-{\i1}san{\i0}?\NThat wound looked fatal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fine. We healed him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god... I thought he was done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so glad you're alive, Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry I couldn't protect you back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must've really had you worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I survived and made it back,\Nso no need to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hug her already, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's been a while since he's ignored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nagumo! Why'd you kill her?\NShe wasn't even resisting anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amanogawa, you're not mad\Nabout me killing her, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mad at yourself\Nfor not being able to kill her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and pretending you've got\Na better reason for being pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-- No! I'm just saying what\Nanyone else would be saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kill or be killed in this world.\NYou've got to kill your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You murdered her! Of course it's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't show mercy. I always kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna stand in my way\Nand say you don't like that, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if we used to be classmates.\NI won't hesitate to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong, okay?\NI don't think we're friends or comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here because I owed Shirasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I'm gone, it's goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, Myu's hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then let's go find us\Nsomething yummy to eat, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, what the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gathered a force to help the trapped heroes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we never thought you'd return so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we had to believe the contents\Nof Ilwer's letter were true, to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heroes have returned unscathed! Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is who Hajime-{\i1}kun {\i0}is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really change?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}, I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you let me come with you, Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No--I'm coming with you, Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What it takes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about how\Nmuch I care for Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone beat me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense imminent battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got feelings for another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reciprocate yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yue-{\i1}san{\i0}, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So can I still stay by your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you see me that way, I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm not going to let\Nanyone love you more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you why I stand far above you, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me "girl," call me "Kaori."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Yue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your challenge, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry when you lose, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are my eyes okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it looks like there are dark clouds\Nand a lightning dragon behind Yue-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I see a big white face behind miss Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be quite the interesting journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering about this,\Nbut what's this "Papa" business about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really your kid, Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirasaki--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's her mother?!\NYue, Shea-{\i1}san{\i0}, or that pervert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me there are more!\NHow many women did you knock up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:20:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We leave early tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:17.55,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,"Good morning," "Good night,"\Nall those simple things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:22.63,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,are so dreamlike and beloved to me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:27.35,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I finally met you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:33.98,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is so special, thank you again
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it. You've been a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made from the world's strongest metal,\Nmade stronger by condensing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:42.11,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be lonely all by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna find anything\Ntougher or sharper, I guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:47.33,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until you found me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. You're incredible, Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you couldn't fight at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:52.91,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you've used your Synergist\Nskills to do stuff like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll be using it so much,\Nit'll almost become part of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:58.34,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, until I thought of a world without you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:05.18,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?\NI miss you, I'm so fond of you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the last boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Shizuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?! What are you two doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:10.97,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, don't forget it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just thanking her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you looking at me like that?!\NSeriously, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:16.06,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine bright like the first star in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:21.86,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,and stay closer to me than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:27.24,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:32.75,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let go of that hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you known?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:40.11,On Top Italic,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay by my side and shine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a long, long time.\NKaori's always held a candle for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going anywhere, are you, Shizuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Kaorin! I'll always be on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Suzu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, Eri-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off you go, now. Go to Nagumo-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuku-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what is that?!\NI've never seen anything like it before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Hajime-{\i1}kun{\i0},\Nwhy are we all sitting like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it always is!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.19,0:22:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yue-{\i1}san {\i0}always gets to sit next to him,\Nbut one day, I'm gonna sit there, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tio-{\i1}san{\i0}, you're really all right\Nwith this arrangement?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.24,0:22:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I'm all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, this sort of treatment is what\Nreally gets me all hot and bothered inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a pervert, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:22:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sexy neglecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.79,0:23:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myu, where the hell\Ndid you learn that word?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Myself as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.30,0:23:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what? Why did she just lick her lips?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find my way home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take Yue and the others with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who gets in the way\Nof that is my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they're my enemy, I'll kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they happen to be a god.